title: The John Zink Hamworthy Combustion Handbook, Second Edition: Vol
description:
English | 2013 | ISBN: 1439839646 | ISBN-13: 9781439839645 | 572 pages | PDF | 110 MB

Despite the length of time it has been around, its importance, and vast amounts of research, combustion is still far from being completely understood. 

Issues regarding the environment, cost, and fuel consumption add further complexity, particularly in the process and power generation industries.
